    "created_at": "2015-07-07T18:52:47Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-07-07T18:52:47Z",
    "body": "I think what @adhithyan15 is trying to say here is that atom is not capturing the usage of the Alt/Option key as an Alt/Meta/Option key so none of the keychords mapped to alt in the atom editor are working on the mac. The option key on the mac is usually used for typing special characters or symbols and it's still doing that by default.\n"
